Pitney Bowes Inc said Mountain Bell, aunit of US West Inc &lt;USW>, began a test of a new Pitney Bowescomputerized mail processing system.    The test has been approved by the U.S. Postal Service, thecompany said.    The processing and postage payment system allows faster andless costly mail preparation, automated funds transfer to coverpostage charges and a production and funds tracking system, itsaid.    Mountain Bell processes more than 19 mln pieces of mailannually. Reuter&#3;